Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我和克里斯一起工作， \N {\rENG} I worked with Chris
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得有这么多美好 \N {\rENG} and I felt like there was just so much goodness
