Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我感到非常强烈的愿望 \N {\rENG} and I felt a very strong desire to come
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,有点只是尝试帮助公司发展 \N {\rENG} and sort of just try to help make the company
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,更实用一点。 \N {\rENG} a little more functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我记得最后，在我们完成 GPT-3 之后， \N {\rENG} - I remember towards the end  after we'd done GPT-3
