Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且，你知道，一旦保罗在一起做某事， \N {\rENG} And  you know  once Paul had something together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,在他宣布这个概念后几乎立即， \N {\rENG} then pretty much immediately after he announced the concept
