Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.00,0:30:37.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就像 \N {\rENG} and that would just be like
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.00,0:30:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,事情出错真是令人悲伤，对吧？ \N {\rENG} a really sad way for things to go wrong  right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.00,0:30:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这只是关于操作它， \N {\rENG} It's just all about operationalizing it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.00,0:30:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,使人们易于理解。 \N {\rENG} making it easy for people to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.00,0:30:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的，我想说的是 \N {\rENG} - Yeah  the thing I would say is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.00,0:30:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们谁都不想成立一家公司。 \N {\rENG} none of us wanted to found a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.00,0:30:49.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们只是觉得这是我们的责任，对吗？ \N {\rENG} We just felt like it was our duty  right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.00,0:30:51.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 感觉我们必须这样做。 \N {\rENG} - It felt like we had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.00,0:30:52.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 就像，我们必须做这件事。 \N {\rENG} - Like  we have to do this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.00,0:30:55.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是我们利用人工智能让事情变得更好的方式。 \N {\rENG} This is the way we're gonna make things go better with AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.00,0:30:57.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这也是我们做出承诺的原因，对吧？ \N {\rENG} Like that's also why we did the pledge  right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.00,0:30:59.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的。 - 因为我们就像 \N {\rENG} - Yeah. - Because we're like
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.00,0:31:01.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们这样做的原因是感觉这是我们的责任。 \N {\rENG} the reason we're doing this is it feels like our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.00,0:31:05.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我想发明和发现事物 \N {\rENG} - I wanted to invent and discover things
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.00,0:31:06.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以某种有益的方式。 \N {\rENG} in some kind of beneficial way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.00,0:31:10.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是我的想法，这导致了我对人工智能的研究， \N {\rENG} That was how I came to it  and that led to working on AI
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.00,0:31:12.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,人工智能需要大量的工程技术 \N {\rENG} and AI required a lot of engineering
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.00,0:31:15.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,最终人工智能需要大量资金， \N {\rENG} and eventually AI required a lot of capital
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.00,0:31:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我发现的是 \N {\rENG} but what I found was that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.00,0:31:22.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你不这样做 \N {\rENG} if you don't do this in a way where
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.00,0:31:23.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在设置环境， \N {\rENG} you're setting the environment
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.00,0:31:26.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,您在哪里设立公司， \N {\rENG} where you set up the company
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.00,0:31:27.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后很多事情就完成了 \N {\rENG} then a lot of it gets done
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.00,0:31:30.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,很多人都在重复同样的错误 \N {\rENG} a lot of it repeats the same mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:35.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我发现科技界是如此疏远。 \N {\rENG} that I found so alienating about the tech community.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.00,0:31:36.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,都是同一群人， \N {\rENG} It's the same people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:38.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,都是一样的态度 \N {\rENG} it's the same attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.00,0:31:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是相同的模式匹配， \N {\rENG} it's the same pattern-matching
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.00,0:31:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以在某些时候这似乎是不可避免的 \N {\rENG} And so at some point it just seemed inevitable
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.00,0:31:44.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们需要以不同的方式来做这件事。 \N {\rENG} that we need to do it in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 当我们在研究生院闲逛时 \N {\rENG} - When we were hanging out in graduate school
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.00,0:31:48.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我记得你有这样的整个计划 \N {\rENG} I remember you had kind of this whole program
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.00,0:31:50.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,试图弄清楚如何做科学 \N {\rENG} of trying to figure out how to do science
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.00,0:31:52.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以某种方式促进公共利益。 \N {\rENG} in a way that would sort of advance the public good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.00,0:31:54.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为这非常类似于 \N {\rENG} And I think that's pretty similar to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.00,0:31:57.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们如何看待这个问题。 \N {\rENG} how we we think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.00,0:31:59.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想你有类似 Vannevar 计划之类的东西， \N {\rENG} I think you had this like Project Vannevar or something
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.00,0:32:01.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样做。 \N {\rENG} to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.00,0:32:02.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是一名教授。 \N {\rENG} I was a professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.00,0:32:04.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想基本上我只是看看情况 \N {\rENG} I think basically I just looked at the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.00,0:32:06.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我确信人工智能 \N {\rENG} and I was convinced that AI
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.00,0:32:09.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,处于非常非常陡峭的轨道上 \N {\rENG} was on a very  very  very steep trajectory
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.00,0:32:10.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,就影响力而言， \N {\rENG} in terms of impact
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.00,0:32:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,看起来并不是因为需要资本， \N {\rENG} didn't seem like because of the necessity for capital
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.00,0:32:16.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,作为一名物理学教授，我可以继续这样做 \N {\rENG} and as a physics professor  I could continue doing that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.00,0:32:20.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有点想和我信任的人一起工作 \N {\rENG} and I kind of wanted to work with people that I trusted
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.00,0:32:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,建立一个机构来努力让人工智能顺利发展。 \N {\rENG} in building an institution to try to make AI go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:29.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是，是的，我永远不会建议成立一家公司。 \N {\rENG} But yeah  I would never recommend founding a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.00,0:32:30.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者说真的很想做。 \N {\rENG} Or really want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.00,0:32:32.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，是的，我认为这只是达到目的的一种手段。 \N {\rENG} I mean  yeah  I think it's just a means to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.00,0:32:33.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是说， \N {\rENG} I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.00,0:32:35.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过，我认为事情通常都会顺利进行。 \N {\rENG} I think that's like usually how things go well  though.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.00,0:32:37.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你做某事只是为了有点像 \N {\rENG} If you're doing something just to sort of like
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.00,0:32:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,充实自己或获得权力，或者， \N {\rENG} enrich yourself or gain power or  like
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.00,0:32:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你必须真正关心 \N {\rENG} you have to sort of actually care about
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,实现世界上真正的目标 \N {\rENG} accomplishing a real goal in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.00,0:32:46.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后你就会找到你所需要的一切手段。 \N {\rENG} and then you find whatever means you have to.
