Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.00,0:33:13.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许是 Anthropic 最值得骄傲的， \N {\rENG} and probably the most proud of at Anthropic
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.00,0:33:16.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,是它对很多人的影响有多好。 \N {\rENG} is how well that has scaled to a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.00,0:33:18.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我感觉就像在这个团体中 \N {\rENG} It feels to me like in this group
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.00,0:33:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以及其他领导层， \N {\rENG} and with the rest of leadership
