Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.00,0:35:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者认为公司的其他部门 \N {\rENG} or think that other parts of the company
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.00,0:35:36.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在试图破坏他们正在做的事情。 \N {\rENG} are trying to undermine what they're doing.
