Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.00,0:35:38.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我认为最重要的是 \N {\rENG} - And I think the most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.00,0:35:40.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们设法保存的是， \N {\rENG} we've managed to preserve is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.00,0:35:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,再说一次，像 RSP 这样的东西推动它， \N {\rENG} and again  things like the RSP drive it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.00,0:35:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个想法不是，你知道， \N {\rENG} this idea that it's not  you know
