Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.00,0:35:50.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以及公司的其他部门试图修复它， \N {\rENG} and other parts of the company trying to repair it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.00,0:35:52.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但公司有不同的部门 \N {\rENG} but that there are different parts of the company
