Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.00,0:36:30.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为这就是 \N {\rENG} And I think it was something that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.00,0:36:32.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我当时很漂亮，很不情愿。 \N {\rENG} I was pretty  pretty reluctant for.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.00,0:36:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也想，当我们离开时， \N {\rENG} And I think  as well  when we did leave
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.00,0:36:38.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想我当时不愿意创办一家公司。 \N {\rENG} I think I was  you know  I was reluctant to start a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.00,0:36:40.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想我已经争论了很长时间了 \N {\rENG} I think I was arguing for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.00,0:36:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们应该做一个非营利组织 \N {\rENG} that we should do a nonprofit instead
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.00,0:36:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,并专注于安全研究。 \N {\rENG} and just focus on safety research.
