Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.00,0:36:46.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我认为这确实需要实用主义 \N {\rENG} - And I think it really took pragmatism
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.00,0:36:49.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,并面对限制 \N {\rENG} and confronting the constraints
