Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.00,0:36:53.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,为了完成这个使命—— \N {\rENG} for accomplishing that mission-
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.00,0:36:54.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 嗯嗯。 \N {\rENG} - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.00,0:36:55.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 这导致了人择。 \N {\rENG} - That led to Anthropic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.00,0:36:57.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我认为这是一个非常重要的教训 \N {\rENG} - I think just a really important lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.00,0:36:59.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们一开始就很擅长 \N {\rENG} that we were good about early on
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:02.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是少做承诺，多兑现承诺。 \N {\rENG} is make less promises and keep more of them.
