Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.00,0:37:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,比任何特定政策都更重要。 \N {\rENG} are more important than any particular policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.00,0:37:15.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的。 \N {\rENG} - Yeah.
