Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.00,0:37:28.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后还看到 Vinay 说， \N {\rENG} but also then to watch Vinay sort of say like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.00,0:37:31.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,“好吧，我们必须为企业做正确的事情。 \N {\rENG} "Okay  we have to do the right thing for the business.
