Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.00,0:37:48.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,在这里工作最特别的事情之一 \N {\rENG} one of the most special things about working here
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.00,0:37:52.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是每个人都团结一致，优先考虑实用主义， \N {\rENG} is everybody with that unity is prioritizing the pragmatism
