Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.00,0:38:10.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道，有一群人只看到大事 \N {\rENG} you have a bunch of people who only see a big  you know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.00,0:38:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,安全就像“我们总是必须这样做” \N {\rENG} safety is like  "We always have to do this "
