Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.00,0:38:15.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,研究就像，你知道， \N {\rENG} and research is like  you know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.00,0:38:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,“这是我们唯一关心的事情。” \N {\rENG} "This is the only thing we care about."
