Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.00,0:48:15.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那里有这种共识，再一次， \N {\rENG} where there's this kind of consensus that  again
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.00,0:48:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,看似共识， \N {\rENG} seems like consensus
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.00,0:48:18.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,似乎每个聪明人都这么认为 \N {\rENG} seems like what everyone wise thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.00,0:48:21.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后它就破裂了， \N {\rENG} and then it just kind of breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.00,0:48:23.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我认为这即将发生的地方 \N {\rENG} and so places where I think that's about to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.00,0:48:25.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但这还没有发生。 \N {\rENG} and it hasn't happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.00,0:48:27.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,其中之一是可解释性。 \N {\rENG} One of them is interpretability.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.00,0:48:30.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为可解释性是关键 \N {\rENG} I think interpretability is both the key to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.00,0:48:33.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,指导和制作安全的人工智能系统， \N {\rENG} steering and making safe AI systems
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.00,0:48:35.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们即将明白， \N {\rENG} and we're about to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.00,0:48:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,可解释性包含关于 \N {\rENG} and interpretability contains insights about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.00,0:48:40.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,智能优化问题 \N {\rENG} intelligent optimization problems
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.00,0:48:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以及人类大脑如何运作。 \N {\rENG} and about how the human brain works.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.00,0:48:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我说过了，我真的不是在开玩笑， \N {\rENG} I've said  and I'm really not joking
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.00,0:48:48.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯·奥拉将成为未来的诺贝尔医学奖获得者。 \N {\rENG} Chris Olah is gonna be a future Nobel Medicine Laureate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.00,0:48:49.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 哦，是的。 \N {\rENG} - Aw  yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.00,0:48:50.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我是认真的。 \N {\rENG} - I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.00,0:48:51.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是认真的， \N {\rENG} I'm serious
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.00,0:48:53.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为其中很多， \N {\rENG} because a lot of these
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.00,0:48:54.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我曾经是一名神经科学家 \N {\rENG} I used to be a neuroscientist
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.00,0:48:56.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,很多这样的心理疾病， \N {\rENG} a lot of these mental illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.00,0:48:58.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些我们还没有弄清楚的，对吧， \N {\rENG} the ones we haven't figured out  right
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.00,0:49:00.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,精神分裂症或情绪障碍， \N {\rENG} schizophrenia or the mood disorders
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.00,0:49:04.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我怀疑有一些更高级别的系统正在发生 \N {\rENG} I suspect there's some higher level system thing going on
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.00,0:49:06.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,很难理解那些有头脑的人 \N {\rENG} and that it's hard to make sense of those with brains
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.00,0:49:08.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为大脑太软了 \N {\rENG} because brains are so mushy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.00,0:49:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,并且很难敞开心扉并与之互动。 \N {\rENG} and hard to open up and interact with.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.00,0:49:12.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,神经网络不是这样的； \N {\rENG} Neural nets are not like this;
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.00,0:49:13.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,它们并不是一个完美的类比， \N {\rENG} they're not a perfect analogy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.00,0:49:16.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但随着时间的推移，它们将成为更好的类比。 \N {\rENG} but as time goes on  they will be a better analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.00,0:49:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是一个区域。 \N {\rENG} That's one area.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.00,0:49:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,其次，与此相关的是， \N {\rENG} Second is  related to that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.00,0:49:22.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为人工智能在生物学中的应用。 \N {\rENG} I think just the use of AI for biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.00,0:49:26.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,生物学是一个极其困难的问题。 \N {\rENG} Biology is an incredibly difficult problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.00,0:49:31.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,由于多种原因，人们仍然持怀疑态度。 \N {\rENG} People continue to be skeptical  for a number of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.00,0:49:33.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为这种共识正在开始被打破。 \N {\rENG} I think that consensus is starting to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.00,0:49:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们看到了诺贝尔化学奖 \N {\rENG} We saw a Nobel Prize in chemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.00,0:49:37.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,因 AlphaFold 获奖；非凡的成就。 \N {\rENG} awarded for AlphaFold; remarkable accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.00,0:49:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们应该尝试建造一些东西 \N {\rENG} We should be trying to build things
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.00,0:49:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这可以帮助我们创建一百个 AlphaFold。 \N {\rENG} that can help us create a hundred AlphaFolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.00,0:49:46.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,最后，利用人工智能加强民主。 \N {\rENG} And then finally  using AI to enhance democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.00,0:49:49.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们担心人工智能是否以错误的方式构建， \N {\rENG} We worry about if AI is built in the wrong way
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.00,0:49:52.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,它可以成为威权主义的工具。 \N {\rENG} it can be a tool for authoritarianism.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.00,0:49:56.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,人工智能如何成为自由和自决的工具？ \N {\rENG} How can AI be a tool for freedom and self-determination?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.00,0:49:59.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为其中一个比其他两个早， \N {\rENG} I think that one is earlier than the other two
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.00,0:50:01.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但这同样重要。 \N {\rENG} but it's gonna be just as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.00,0:50:04.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的，我的意思是，我猜有两件事 \N {\rENG} - Yeah  I mean  I guess two things that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:05.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少连接到你之前所说的， \N {\rENG} at least connect to what you were saying earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.00,0:50:12.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，一是我觉得人们经常加入 Anthropic \N {\rENG} I mean  one is I feel like people frequently join Anthropic
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.00,0:50:13.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为他们有点像 \N {\rENG} because they're sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.00,0:50:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,从科学角度来说，对人工智能真的很好奇 \N {\rENG} scientifically really curious about AI
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.00,0:50:21.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后有点被人工智能的进步所说服 \N {\rENG} and then kind of get convinced by AI progress
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.00,0:50:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,分享需求的愿景， \N {\rENG} to sort of share the vision of the need
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.00,0:50:26.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,不只是为了进步技术， \N {\rENG} not just to advance the technology
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.00,0:50:28.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但要更深入地理解它 \N {\rENG} but to understand it more deeply
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.00,0:50:31.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,并确保其安全。 \N {\rENG} and to make sure that it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.00,0:50:33.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得这实际上有点令人兴奋 \N {\rENG} And I feel like it's actually just sort of exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.00,0:50:36.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,与你一起工作的人 \N {\rENG} to have people that you're working with
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.00,0:50:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们的愿景越来越一致 \N {\rENG} kind of more and more united in their vision
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.00,0:50:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,人工智能开发的样子 \N {\rENG} for both what AI development looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.00,0:50:44.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以及与之相关的责任感。 \N {\rENG} and the sort of sense of responsibility associated with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.00,0:50:46.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得这样的事情已经发生了很多次 \N {\rENG} And I feel like that's been happening a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.00,0:50:47.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,由于很多进步 \N {\rENG} due to a lot of advances
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.00,0:50:48.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,去年发生的事情， \N {\rENG} that have happened in the last year
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.00,0:50:50.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像汤姆所说的那样。 \N {\rENG} like what Tom talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.00,0:50:51.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,另一个是，我的意思是， \N {\rENG} Another is that  I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.00,0:50:53.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,回到具体问题， \N {\rENG} going back really to concrete problems
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.00,0:50:56.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们在人工智能安全方面做了很多工作 \N {\rENG} I feel like we've done a lot of work on AI safety
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.00,0:50:57.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,到目前为止。 \N {\rENG} up until this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.00,0:50:59.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,很多确实很重要 \N {\rENG} A lot of it's really important
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.00,0:51:01.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我认为我们现在，随着最近的一些进展， \N {\rENG} but I think we're now  with some recent developments
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.00,0:51:04.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,真正了解什么样的风险 \N {\rENG} really getting a glimmer of what kinds of risks
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.00,0:51:06.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能确实来自系统 \N {\rENG} might literally come about from systems
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.00,0:51:07.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是非常非常先进的—— \N {\rENG} that are very  very advanced-
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.00,0:51:08.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 嗯嗯。 \N {\rENG} - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.00,0:51:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 以便我们可以调查和研究它们 \N {\rENG} - So that we can investigate and study them
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.00,0:51:13.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,直接具有可解释性， \N {\rENG} directly with interpretability
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.00,0:51:15.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,与其他类型的安全机制， \N {\rENG} with other kinds of safety mechanisms
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.00,0:51:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,并真正了解其中的风险 \N {\rENG} and really understand what the risks from
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.00,0:51:21.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,非常先进的人工智能可能看起来像。 \N {\rENG} very advanced AI might look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.00,0:51:23.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为这就是 \N {\rENG} And I think that that's something that is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.00,0:51:26.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,真的会让我们进一步完成使命 \N {\rENG} really gonna allow us to sort of further the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.00,0:51:29.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以一种非常深入的科学、实证的方式。 \N {\rENG} in a really deeply scientific  empirical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.00,0:51:31.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我对接下来的六个月感到兴奋 \N {\rENG} And so I'm excited about sort of the next six months of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.00,0:51:33.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们如何运用我们的理解 \N {\rENG} how we use our understanding of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.00,0:51:37.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,先进系统可能会出现什么问题来表征 \N {\rENG} what can go wrong with advanced systems to characterize that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.00,0:51:40.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,并弄清楚如何避免这些陷阱。 \N {\rENG} and figure out how to avoid those pitfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.00,0:51:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 完美的。 \N {\rENG} - Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.00,0:51:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,鳍！ - 耶！ \N {\rENG} Fin! - Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.00,0:51:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我们做到了！ \N {\rENG} - We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.00,0:51:44.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 哇！ \N {\rENG} - Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.00,0:51:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好时光。 - 我知道。 \N {\rENG} - Good time. - I know.
